title Activity Diagram: Rendering Loop

|Developer|
start
:Start render loop;

|FlowJS|
repeat
  :Update controls;
  :Update animations;
  
  |updateManager|
  :Update all LODs;
  :Switch detail levels;
  
  |Renderer|
  :Render frame;
  
repeat while (Running?)

|Developer|
stop
@enduml